narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend BRST 322 to another student, though it is probably only a Yale-in-London thing, and I would not recommend that program as a whole (study abroad in London, but go to an actual university). Prof Mitchell is very engaging and easy-going, and the material is interesting.
Absolutely. LESLIE MITCHELL IS AMAZING. You will learn so much in this course.
IT WAS SUPERAWESOME. Seriously it was like the only real class.
